    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like things will ever be okay again. nothing feels real. i look at everything in this house and it just feels like i'm living in a museum of a life that's already over. i'm just tired. i'm so incredibly tired of everything. it feels like the pain is the only thing that's actually real anymore.",
