      "content": "i know people say it gets better but i don't think i want it to. staying here feels like i'm just waiting for nothing. sometimes i think if i could just go where he is, the weight would finally lift. it feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just... stop. to not have to wake up to this silence anymore.",
